==Dependencies==

* HFST
* VISLCG3
* Lttoolbox
* Apertium

==Installation==

Run:

$ ./autogen.sh

then

$ make

Now test the translator with:

$ echo "Ahmet biralarını var." | apertium -d . tr-az
  Ahmet pivələrini var.

==Development==

* If you want to develop with this pair, you will need to check out 
  both 'azmorph'[1] and 'TRmorph'[2]

* Do not make any direct changes to the files in morph-az and morph-tr,
  the file 'update-lexica.py' can be used to update these if you have 
  changed the bilingual dictionary.

;Notes

1. https://apertium.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/apertium/branches/azmorph
2. https://github.com/coltekin/TRmorph
